\vspace{0.8cm}

{\large\itshape
The gap between developers who thrive in California\\
and those who fail is not intelligence, capital, or connections.\\[6pt]
It is \textbf{operational fluency} --- the ability to navigate\\
California's regulatory labyrinth at speed.}

\vspace{1cm}

